Schutt Sports Wins Court Approval of Riddell Settlement

-- B y   M i c h a e l   B a t h o n
-- 
2011-02-11T20:43:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/schutt-sports-wins-court-approval-of-riddell-settlement.html
Schutt Sports Inc. won court
approval of a settlement with Riddell Inc., ending their legal
dispute over football-helmet infringement and setting Schutt on
the path to exit bankruptcy.  The bankruptcy case is In re Schutt Sports Inc., 10-12795,  U.S. Bankruptcy Court , District of  Delaware  (Wilmington).  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael Bathon in Wilmington, Delaware, at 
 mbathon@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David E. Rovella at   drovella@bloomberg.net . 